\fIid\fP \- add request ID to the context

.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
\fIid\fP adds a random request ID to the context. Other handlers such as \fIlog\fP use it in the logging if present.

.SH "SYNTAX"
.PP
.RS

.nf
id

.fi
.RE

.SH "EXAMPLES"
.PP
.RS

.nf
